snippet: State Senator Kwame Raoul said actuarial studies of various proposals, including recent ones submitted by the governor, would take more time.
abstract: Illinois legislative committee seeking compromise plan to rein in state's huge unfunded public pension liability will not meet deadline set by Gov Pat Quinn.
lead_paragraph: State Senator Kwame Raoul said actuarial studies of various proposals, including recent ones submitted by the governor, would take more time.

headline.main: Illinois: Panel Says It Will Miss Pension Plan Deadline
headline.print_headline: Illinois: Panel Says It Will Miss Pension Plan Deadline
